title: Looking for a top laner main silver + is fine
body:
Looking for a top laner main silver level + to join my team. I have been adding new players to form a team that will grow! If you are looking for a team to be good mates and ranked 5 together then come join. My team is gold 5 in rank! 

My ign is Demonsiayer

replies.body:
I main top and support, if your interested let me know.
And also let me know of when so I get set up.

People have a habit of making me busy when I don't want to be.
